<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3744] [DS] Component should set implementation object before propagating changed service properties</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3744</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A component needs to set its implementation object before propagating the service property changes from the activate method.  Otherwise the new service properties could satisfy a target filter and result in a getService() request before the implementation object is set but after it has been created.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
